Peregrine Falcon

  • Did you know peregrine falcons can go 200 or 250 or somewhere in the middle?
  • When they are just normally flying 50 or 60 miles per hour and when they go 200 or 250 or somewhere in the middle that's called a stoop.
  • They are the fastest thing on earth.
  • Their wings are strong and when they stop they stop by putting their wings out.
